{"tid":1568733,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"踩場＝撐場","createTime":"2019-09-14T11:12:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T11:44:34.000Z","uid":108502,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e404031e67077b4d108e8ea7ef8b1e90738396cb","tid":1568733,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:12:13.000Z","msg":"本身百幾個廢老去唱支那歌係WFC<br />\n連新聞都未必會上，根本唔會有人知<br />\n<br />\n但係去踩場打大交就變大新聞，全香港都討論佢哋<br />\n百幾條撚樣做到幾千人都未必做到嘅宣傳效果<br />\n本身佢哋可能鳩鳩下唱完就走<br />\n去踩場就刺激到佢哋想更加積極行動，下次冇錢收都照出嚟報仇<br />\n<br />\n下次有呢類藍絲活動就嗌人唔好接近嗰頭好過<br />\n唔好再吹雞踩場"},{"pid":"c04dfb7e0905e955f49e86c87324860d7ce6f725","tid":1568733,"uid":101963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:12:46.000Z","msg":"對付藍絲應該借力打力，順水推舟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568616\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568616</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"be332d3fae8d3f97d4ba71d2970a23a52cb472a1","tid":1568733,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:14:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fa14726cdd743bfbcc36c9eac97ba0c6a53acf9","tid":1568733,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:16:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bf9c0eab296ea716b802eef159753523d0375eb5","tid":1568733,"uid":108337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:17:12.000Z","msg":"要圍觀都去遠啲呀，咁近比人count埋一齊好似好多人咁"},{"pid":"ee1bf95bed4c5a27c867196ce1f77c7e2ca245c5","tid":1568733,"uid":271235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:18:31.000Z","msg":"應該話藍屍狗一統一衣著就要非常小心"},{"pid":"20b294df89af7c9476e5843110276bebca997d62","tid":1568733,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:21:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38c43a72f9c9294463fbbd7e2e2e5c300c543723","tid":1568733,"uid":78295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sc